<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_105" id="51v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_105_r1l1">Frawn Annen von vveinſperg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l2">geborn von Hohenloch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_105_r1l3">Edle lıebe frawe . als vns eẅr edel <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat wıe etlıch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> kawff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l4">leẅt vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / dıe ſtraſſen für vffenheim / durch eẅr geleyt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l5">mıt <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> leẅt geleyt faren vnd ſıch geleyten <expan>laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> etc das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l6">wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu ıſt vns nıht <expan>wıſſenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> welh dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das getan </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l7"><expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ wır ſıe nıht <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wıſſen ʒu <expan>beſend<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mıt Jn <expan>dauo<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l8">ʒu reden / Auch ſınd ſıe nıht alle dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> / dıe <expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> ſtraſſe faren </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l9">Denn wo wır <expan>eẅr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lıeb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dıenſt etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_105_r1l10"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> ij<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> Oculȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_105" id="51v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Frawn Annen von Weinsperg, geborn von Hohenloch </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Edle liebe frawe, als uns ewr edel <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> hat
                        wie etlich <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> kawfflewt und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> die strassen für Uffenheim durch ewr
                        geleyt mit <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> lewt geleyt faren und sich
                        geleyten <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                        Nu ist uns niht <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> welh die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> das getan
                            <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir sie niht
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wissen zu <expan>besend<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> mit in <expan>davo<ex>n</ex></expan> zu reden;
                        auch sind sie niht alle die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die
                                <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> strasse faren. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> edel lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        dienst etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> ii<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> oculi.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
